<br>
If you need a massive stunner or immune cold, go with 61 air.<br>
<br>
If you can position a pet behind the mob and pet does not tank, use 62 water.  Or if you need immune poison use this pet.<br>
<br>
Forget 63 fire if your not dueling, he suxxor.  Should be immune fire, not sure.<br>
<br>
If you need root, use 65 earth.  Or if you need immune disease.<br>
<br>
PoP pets fair better then epic on very high level mob due to resists.  But epic JUST FLAT OUT has some advantages.<br>
<br>
The 50 point DS you don't need to refresh.<br>
The 143 damage proc that goes off alot.<br>
Highest base HP.<br>
Holds aggro over other pets due to Procs + Lower level.<br>
Always runs at SoW speed<br>
<br>
Edit: yes before you other mages say it, when I say &quot;immune&quot; I mean just very resistant.<br>
